<http://www.loa-cnr.it/ontologies/DUL.owl#isDescribedBy> owl:equivalentProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/lachi/ontologies/2026/nameholder#isDescribedBy> .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/lachi/ontologies/2026/nameholder#describes
<http://www.semanticweb.org/lachi/ontologies/2026/nameholder#describes> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                                                        owl:inverseOf <http://www.semanticweb.org/lachi/ontologies/2026/nameholder#isDescribedBy> .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/lachi/ontologies/2026/nameholder#hasAgent
