                                                                                  rdfs:range <http://www.semanticweb.org/lachi/ontologies/2026/nameholder#EthicalRule> ,
                                                                                             <http://www.semanticweb.org/lachi/ontologies/2026/nameholder#ExpectedSocialFrame> ,
                                                                                             <http://www.semanticweb.org/lachi/ontologies/2026/nameholder#SubversiveFrame> ;
                                                                                  rdfs:comment "All the elements that, blended, make the DescriptionFrame of the humor" .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/lachi/ontologies/2026/nameholder#includesSituation
